headline: Interactive Brokers Launches Stablecoin Funding for Retail Accounts
summary: Interactive Brokers Group Inc. (IBKR: US) has begun allowing retail clients to fund individual brokerage accounts with stablecoins, adding a crypto-native onboarding option alongside traditional bank transfers for its extensive client base. The broker said the capability is being rolled out gradually, starting with a subset of eligible US customers, ...
